videos.headline: UT Martin's Winn tosses 16-yard TD pass
videos.description: Dresser Winn lofts a 16-yard pass to teammate Devonte Howard for opening touchdown

videos.headline: Middle Tennessee's Windham catches second TD of the 1st quarter
videos.description: Brent Stockstill floats a pass up that CJ Windham high-points and bring in for a 10-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: UT Martin ties it with 11-yard passing TD
videos.description: Dresser Winn throws an 11-yard dart to Terry Williams in the back of the end zone to tie the game.
